   Duke J 1975 pp 9 [PH, RAIN, TEMP]
   Purseglove J 1974 pp 92 [USE]
   Janick J 1991 pp 384
   Hornok L 1992 pp 233-235 [RAIN, KTMP, TEXT, PH, FER, USE]

